Dialogue: 5,0:02:04.39,0:02:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm the only one who lives in this place.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:23.09,0:02:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:25.04,0:02:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there's something else here that I can't see.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:33.62,0:02:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you... for the food.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:37.14,0:02:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After all this time, I don't find it that scary anymore.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:43.80,0:02:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It must be some sort of deity or god, I think.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:52.70,0:02:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In this place, it's always nighttime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:06.12,Mushisode Title,,0,0,0,eptitle,{\fad(2000,0)\an7\bord0\blur0.6\p1\c&HAC94A9&\pos(-2,66)\fscx600\fscy90}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100
Dialogue: 2,0:03:00.11,0:03:06.12,Mushisode Title,,0,0,0,eptitle,{\fad(2000,0)\an4\blur0.6\pos(70,108)}A Sea of Otherworldly Stars
Dialogue: 5,0:03:20.69,0:03:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:22.17,0:03:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My doll is gone.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:24.91,0:03:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have hidden it again.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:36.59,0:03:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:39.14,0:03:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I won again today!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:52.26,0:03:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:10.40,0:04:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what lies beyond that sky.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:20.09,0:04:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe everyone went someplace beyond the sky,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:23.38,0:04:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and that's the reason there's nobody here now.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:47.15,0:04:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This all seems so familiar.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:48.88,0:04:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel like I've seen a tiny starry sky like that before.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:07.15,0:05:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But in this place,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:13.09,0:05:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}everything is just so beautiful and so comfortable.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:20.90,0:05:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compared to {that}it, even remembering \Nmy past seems like nothing but a chore.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:40.27,0:05:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:43.42,0:05:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:46.09,0:05:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Izumi here?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:49.68,0:05:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who's he?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:52.62,0:05:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming in.{Pardon the intrusion.}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:57.48,0:05:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:59.00,0:06:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone here?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:02.97,0:06:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, what a huge house.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:05.95,0:06:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:08.26,0:06:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems I'm out of time already.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:12.39,0:06:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:13.93,0:06:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)}I'd better increase the dosage next time...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:22.98,0:06:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Where could he have gone?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:37.91,0:06:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:40.66,0:06:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Found you.{like moths to the flame.}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.48,0:06:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mizuho.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:50.69,0:06:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:54.21,0:06:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing with Izumi.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:57.15,0:06:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Not you too. Enough already.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:00.45,0:07:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop that nonsense.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:02.05,0:07:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother's asked over \Nanother one of those strange people, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:07.60,0:07:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:08.82,0:07:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi was kidnapped, by a real person.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:12.41,0:07:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise I'll find whoever did it,
Dialogue: 5,0:07:14.53,0:07:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,so cut all this out already.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:18.41,0:07:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:20.79,0:07:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I really did see her.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:24.60,0:07:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You just dreamed that up!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:27.37,0:07:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There was nothing at the bottom of that well.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:53.92,0:07:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ginko?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:55.84,0:07:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:56.90,0:07:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:59.25,0:08:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it go?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:00.55,0:08:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find Izumi?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:01.61,0:08:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I unfortunately ran out of time.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:05.81,0:08:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:09.34,0:08:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can say for sure \Nthat your daughter is alive and in this house.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:15.70,0:08:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're simply unable to perceive each other right now.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:21.32,0:08:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,However, one must exercise caution \Nwhen synchronizing with the other side.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:27.01,0:08:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone were to stay there too long,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:29.17,0:08:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,they might forget to return as well...{"as well" is intentionally vague here in my edit. It could be "just like Izumi forgot" or "forget to return just like forgetting other memories."}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:32.89,0:08:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,especially if they're {someone }attuned to that side.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:39.52,0:08:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I will try again first thing tomorrow.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:57.00,0:08:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi's...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:00.04,0:09:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,here after all, isn't she?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:03.96,0:09:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You may not be able to see her, but she is.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:10.11,0:09:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:12.68,0:09:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see her?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:15.25,0:09:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:17.10,0:09:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But someone always takes my doll.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:22.02,0:09:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi was always doing that,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:24.88,0:09:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,even though she had one of her own.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:28.55,0:09:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So even now, I play with her by hiding my doll.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:52.22,0:09:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone again...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:56.15,0:09:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where could it be today?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:03.84,0:10:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:05.74,0:10:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Found you.{creepy}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:10.35,0:10:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:11.39,0:10:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear me out.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:13.53,0:10:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother asked me to bring you back home.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:17.98,0:10:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You fell into an old well in the woods {out back behind}near your home,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:21.22,0:10:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's how you came to this side.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:29.01,0:10:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:30.80,0:10:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What well?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:32.80,0:10:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This{\i0} is my home!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:36.31,0:10:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,As I suspected, you're definitely attuned to this side.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:42.23,0:10:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.88,0:10:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the place you belong is the place \Nwhere people are waiting for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:50.02,0:10:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond that sky over there, \Nthere are people waiting for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:56.12,0:10:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mom, who makes you food every day...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:59.89,0:11:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Your big sister, who hides that doll and plays with you...{Timing: Generous lead-out, please}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:04.40,0:11:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to remember.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:06.37,0:11:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't where you're supposed to be.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:13.98,0:11:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:14.80,0:11:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm running out of time.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:17.55,0:11:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to take matters into my own hands.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:47.33,0:11:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you do—
Dialogue: 5,0:11:48.28,0:11:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:54.67,0:11:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,300)}Izumi!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:57.85,0:11:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:01.81,0:12:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,150)}Izumi?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:04.39,0:12:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Come back!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:09.80,0:12:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Izumi!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:18.37,0:12:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mizuho.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:22.05,0:12:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There are stars shining at the bottom of the well.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:25.41,0:12:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:27.10,0:12:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:29.40,0:12:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Right there.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:30.60,0:12:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There are so many of them!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:35.17,0:12:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing there...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:37.36,0:12:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, we should go home.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:40.77,0:12:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get in trouble if we play here.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:44.12,0:12:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:47.26,0:12:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm going to leave you behind.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:49.98,0:12:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:51.38,0:12:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait for me!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:08.44,0:13:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi, let's play with my doll.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:12.90,0:13:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:16.58,0:13:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? There aren't as many stars this time.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:22.88,0:13:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, I'll let you borrow it.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:27.15,0:13:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:28.30,0:13:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll just take it back right after anyway.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:32.70,0:13:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll {\i1}give{\i0} you it, then!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:36.36,0:13:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You will?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:37.33,0:13:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:38.35,0:13:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:56.72,0:13:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can you see them?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:58.26,0:13:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:06.87,0:14:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are even fewer of them now.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:12.68,0:14:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi, are you out here?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:49.45,0:14:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing down there.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:52.48,0:14:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all I found.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:56.18,0:14:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be right.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:57.91,0:15:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw Izumi fall in there.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:00.83,0:15:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:04.04,0:15:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuho, you had another fight with Izumi, didn't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:09.75,0:15:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why she ran away.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:13.00,0:15:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi's out there somewhere!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:31.37,0:15:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be okay, Mom.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:33.38,0:15:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in Mr. Ginko.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:38.87,0:15:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:09.19,0:16:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If you see smoke rising up from the well,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:11.24,0:16:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,call down to the bottom of the well.{Repetition, but it makes things clear, so I'm leaving it.}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:15.59,0:16:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. There's still some left.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.27,0:16:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This should be enough.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:29.24,0:16:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to synchronize with Izumi{-san} one more time.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:34.20,0:16:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's likely that she's lost her memories,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:37.25,0:16:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but if she can remember you, she can come back.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:40.91,0:16:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,However, my time will be limited.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:45.41,0:16:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I think I'm running out of time,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:47.12,0:16:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll force a link from the other side to here.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:51.68,0:16:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made the necessary preparations.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:54.95,0:16:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The link will allow Izumi \Nto hear your voices from this side.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:03.33,0:17:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Izumi!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:05.29,0:17:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Izumi!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:06.08,0:17:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Izumi!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:08.53,0:17:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Izumi!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:09.56,0:17:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Izumi!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:10.83,0:17:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Izumi!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:15.03,0:17:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuho...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:17.20,0:17:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:21.89,0:17:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,400)}I'm here!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:27.44,0:17:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)}I'm here!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:32.80,0:17:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Izumi's voice just now!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:35.40,0:17:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She said, "I'm here."
Dialogue: 5,0:17:37.26,0:17:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It came from inside the house!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:43.42,0:17:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the heck is making a bonfire?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:54.07,0:17:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:58.94,0:18:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:00.15,0:18:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi, it's you!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:15.59,0:18:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:25.16,0:18:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the stars have come back, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:29.83,0:18:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But there aren't as many as before.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:36.09,0:18:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:39.22,0:18:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They're called Isei, or "Well Star" mushi.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:42.05,0:18:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,On rare occasions,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:43.29,0:18:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}they appear in wells that are near \Nan abundant flow of vital energy, known as a River of Light.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:50.52,0:18:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Well, I guess one may even liken them to \Nsparks thrown off by the River of Light itself.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:57.19,0:19:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who are exposed to lots of them \Noften go through what you went through.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:03.85,0:19:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason there are fewer of them \Nmay be that the River of Light is meandering.{Keep this comment: As a verb, "to meander" basically means "to wander, usually aimlessly." However, as a river's "meander" has a different meaning (one applicable here as well), I chose the word for its dual application in this line.}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:11.78,0:19:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:15.46,0:19:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But either way,
Dialogue: 5,0:19:17.25,0:19:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,these matters concern \Na world far removed from your own.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:22.40,0:19:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You should bid them farewell.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:29.24,0:19:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:33.17,0:19:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Come now, step aside.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:38.06,0:19:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad,
Dialogue: 5,0:19:39.26,0:19:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't come here anymore, I promise.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:44.62,0:19:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me worry more than I already have.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:54.68,0:19:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, what's that for?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:58.64,0:20:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so the god of the well will still be able to breathe.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:31.61,0:20:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the depths of the earth,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:34.48,0:20:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is it cold?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:36.94,0:20:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it painful?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:39.35,0:20:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it frightening?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:41.60,0:20:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it lonely?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:48.02,0:20:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be that as it may...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:58.87,0:21:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}residing in those very depths
Dialogue: 5,0:21:01.81,0:21:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}are pure water
Dialogue: 5,0:21:04.95,0:21:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fad(0,200)}and a myriad of stars.{Timing: Generous lead-out, please}
